{"tid":510952,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Band招長玩LEAD結他手","createTime":"2017-12-27T03:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T01:19:14.000Z","uid":145109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8efee6fb55c36ffce72520fc2ed2880c35639fa9","tid":510952,"uid":145109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"Band招長玩LEAD結他手，玩左5年<br />\n我地主要年齡為21-24，觀塘有自己band房<br />\n有幾首原創歌，會繼續創作及開始錄歌，並且會參加比賽及爭取不同演出機會。<br />\n本身既歌多為Alternative rock同pop punk，最近想轉玩下Post-hardcore同alternative metal<br />\n故此希望尋找一個有作曲編曲樂理知識既Lead結他手及對以上 Style有一定認識<br />\n而且有責任心, 準時, 每星期練Band。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可telegram: @kgkingsley"},{"pid":"925351592457a5e9303698a45ad761c9d1079546","tid":510952,"uid":145109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5d0680161b08000723149769dc0600ae4298164","tid":510952,"uid":145109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a3f2e8beb5768913a45923aa21394b8d0bf40e2","tid":510952,"uid":145109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"push"}]}